                v1.0.10

                Features:
                    - Explicit begin...commit in resulting diff file.
                    - Explicit quoting has been replaced with quote_ident
                    - Support schema selection using SIMILAR TO instead of LIKE.
                    - Added --use-comments parameter with default value `true`.
                    - Fixed DDL inheritance logic.
                    - Fixed incorrect detection of partition key column during type change.
                    - Support GRANTS management with different behaviors.
                    - Improved speed of execution.
                    - Added execution time to output in seconds.

2026-03-27      v1.0.9

                Features:
                    - Fixed duplicate CREATE INDEX generation for partitions when parent table has an index
                    - Added permissions check for schemas before dump

2026-03-04      v1.0.8

                Features:
                    - Fixed routines flags.
                    - Improved speed of dump creation.

2026-02-27      v1.0.7

                Features:
                    - Partitioning support.
                    - Fixed ordering routines and views.
                    - Fixed serial and bigserial column creation.
                    - Fixed dependency-based ordering of routines for creation and drop.
                    - Fixed work with extensions.

2026-02-19      v1.0.6

                Features:
                    - Partitioning support.

2026-02-16      v1.0.5

                Features:
                    - Fixed support for change owner.
                    - Fixed types drop, because of routine dependencies possible.
                    - Fixed support of composite types.
                    - Fixed primary key names.

2026-01-14      v1.0.4

                Features:
                    - Added support for COMMENTS ON.
                    - Fixed handling of $$ delimiters in SQL routine bodies.
                    - Fixed handling of GENERATED STORED column changes.
                    - Added support for TABLE POLICIES.
                    - Added support for UNIQUE INDEXes.
                    - Fixed order of creation for objects.
                    - Fixed order of object deletion.
                    - Fixed alter column type.

2025-12-22      v1.0.3

                Features:
                    - SQL routines processed at the end of the list, after all others.
                    - Some minimal under the hood improvements.

2025-12-12      v1.0.2

                Features:
                    - Fixed foreign keys ordering.
                    - Fixed TLS connection error.
                    - Fixed naming with special characters.
                    - Added test cases for special characters and composite foreign keys in schema_a.sql and schema_b.sql.
                    - Fixed incorrect transformation of RETURNS TABLE.
                    - Fixed identity columns processing.
                    - Fixed sequence duplication for identity and serial columns.
                    - Fixed creation of partitioned table as a regular table instead of actual partitions.
                    - Fixed DROP scripts for table and table's parts.

2025-11-19      v1.0.1

                Features:
                    - Improved hash workflow.
                    - DROPs are working.

2025-11-07      v1.0.0

                Features:
                    - Initial version: dump, dump compare, run with config.
